( 1.3.6.1.4.1.53622.42.2.4.5 NAME 'mailFilter' DESC 'The entry represents an entity within the organization that can filter email messages according to various policies' SUP top AUXILIARY MAY ( mailAntispamPolicy $ mailAntivirusPolicy $ mailContentPolicy $ cn $ description $ seeAlso ) )
( 1.3.6.1.4.1.53622.42.1.4.1 NAME 'gidObject' DESC 'An object with a POSIX group identifier' SUP top AUXILIARY MUST gid )
( 1.3.6.1.4.1.53622.42.1.4.2 NAME 'posixGroupId' DESC 'Abstraction of a named group of POSIX accounts' SUP posixGroup AUXILIARY MUST gid )
